data.description: Welcome to this 2020 modern farmhouse rambler located in the Windgate at Carrigan Lake neighborhood. Perfectly situated on a .3 acre lot, fully fenced and located on a quiet cul du sac. Upon entering the home you have a spacious, cedar front porch. All living facilities on the main level include a spacious kitchen with white shaker cabinets, a large angular island, SS frigidaire appliances, granite counters and a spacious pantry. The kitchen and informal dining room lead into the open living space with a gas, shiplap fireplace and an abundance of natural light. All three bedrooms are conveniently located on the main level with a full bath. The primary bedroom features vaulted ceilings, a walk in closet and en-suite 3/4 bath. Main floor laundry hosts an LG washer and dryer with wi-fi. Enjoy a "shop" in your garage with the third stall being extra long. Conveniently located near multiple parks, Carrigan Lake, shopping and restaurants. Just 35 miles west of the Twin Cities.
